pokedexEntries.red: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as Hypnosis and Confusion.
pokedexEntries.blue: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as Hypnosis and Confusion.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Avoid eye contact if you come across one. It will try to put you to sleep by using its pendulum.
pokedexEntries.gold: When it is very hungry, it puts humans it meets to sleep, then it feasts on their dreams.
pokedexEntries.silver: Always holding a pendulum that it rocks at a steady rhythm, it causes drowsiness in anyone nearby.
pokedexEntries.crystal: The longer it swings its pendulum, the longer the effects of its hypnosis last.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pokémon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pokémon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
pokedexEntries.emerald: The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum in a Hypno's hand lull the foe into deep hypnosis. While searching for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It carries a pendulum-like device. There once was an incident in which it took away a child it hypnotized.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as Hypnosis and Confusion.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Seeing its swinging pendulum can induce sleep in three seconds, even in someone who just woke up.

pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pokémon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pokémon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum.
pokedexEntries.sun: While it is an extremely dangerous Pokémon, people who are in need of a good, sound sleep call it their savior.
pokedexEntries.moon: As a matter of course, it makes anyone it meets fall asleep and has a taste of their dreams. Anyone having a good dream, it carries off.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: In Alola, Komala is Hypno’s main target. It rarely harms people.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: There are some Hypno that assist doctors with patients who can’t sleep at night in hospitals.
